<p>This article delves into the foundations and core principles of community education in Cardano, exploring effective learning pathways for newcomers and the importance of community involvement in ADA awareness.</p>



<p>We also analyze the role of stake pools in community education and discuss the challenges and innovations in Cardano&#8217;s educational outreach.</p>



