<p>It enables grassroots innovation by providing funding opportunities for community members to propose and develop projects that enhance the Cardano ecosystem.</p>



<p>Through a transparent and decentralized decision-making process, the community collectively decides which projects receive funding, ensuring that the network&#8217;s growth is driven by the needs and aspirations of its stakeholders.</p>



